q <- ggplot(mtcars, aes(x=wt, y=mpg)) + geom_point() +
  ggtitle("Fuel Efficiency of 32 Cars 32   ") +
  xlab("Weight (x1000 lb) ") + ylab("Miles per Gallon   ") +
  theme(title=element_text(family="notosanskr", size = rel(1.2)),
        axis.title=element_text(family="notosanskr", size = rel(0.8)),
        strip.text=element_text(family="notosanskr", size = rel(0.8)))

print(q);

ggsave(filename="foo.pdf", q)
